<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/fonts.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                    <img src="/images/modulelogo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
                </a>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto nav-center">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/"><u>Home</u></a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/community">Community</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/search">The Search</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                        <% if (user) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/playerinfo">
                                <img src="<%= user.playerAvatar %>" alt="Icon" class="icon">
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <% } else { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Sign in</a>
                        </li>
                        <% } %>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>


    <div id="hero-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#hero-carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#hero-carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#hero-carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <section class="hero slide1">
                    <div class="content-wrapper">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h1>The Purdue community has been rattled by the sudden disappearance of Professor Xander, director of the PEARL Lab.</h1>
                            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-warning"><b>JOIN THE HUNT</b></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <section class="hero slide2">
                    <div class="content-wrapper">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h1>Follow the clues and piece together the mystery of Professor Xander's disappearance and the future of AI at Purdue.</h1>
                            <a href="/lab" class="btn btn-warning"><b>EXPLORE LAB</b></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section> 
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <section class="hero slide3">
                    <div class="content-wrapper">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h1>Envision the future of Purdue with AI integrated across campus transforming education and Purdue itself.</h1>
                            <a href="/community" class="btn btn-warning"><b>VIEW COMMUNITY</b></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>


    <section id="community" class="community py-5 bg-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">COMMUNITY</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 community-left">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary mb-4 h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h3>RE-IMAGINING PURDUE</h3>
                            <img src="/images/HomePage - Reimagine Purdue.png" alt="">
                            <p>Dive into a vibrant collection of AI-generated illustrations made by the Purdue community, transforming our campus into stunning, imaginative landscapes.</p>
                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-container">
                            <a href="/community" class="btn btn-warning">CHECK IT OUT</a>
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column">
                    <div class="row flex-grow-1">
                        <div class="col-md-12 mb-4" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                            <div class="card bg-secondary h-100">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h3>INNOVATE WITH AI</h3>
                                    <p>Discover innovative solutions to pressing educational challenges, creatively crafted using AI by our Purdue community.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <div class="card bg-secondary h-100">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h3>AI ACROSS CAMPUS</h3>
                                    <p>Learn about innovative AI initiatives undertaken by students and faculty across the Purdue University campus.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="research" class="research py-5 bg-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>THE RESEARCH LAB</h3>
                    <p>Explore the Professor's lab to discover clues that would help uncover her mysterious disappearance.</p>
                    <img src="/images/home-lab.png" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" style="padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0;">
                    <h3>DR. EMILY XANDER</h3>
                    <p>Dr. Xander, director of PEARL was working on the ground-breaking project ECHO, when tragedy struck.</p>
                    <img src="/images/home-professor.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/search" class="btn btn-warning">FIND OUT WHAT HAPPENED</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="footer">
        <div class="container-fluid" style="padding-bottom: 2%;">
            <h1>Join <b>Mission Renaissance</b> to solve Professor Xander's mystery!</h1>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; background-color: black;">
            <a style="padding: 0 1%;" href="https://github.com/AyanoKen"><i class="fab fa-instagram" style="color: #FFD977; font-size: 3rem;"></i></a>
            <a style="padding: 0 1%;" href="https://github.com/AyanoKen"><i class="fab fa-discord" style="color: #FFD977; font-size: 3rem;"></i></a>
            
            <div style="padding: 2% 0;">

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <% if (!user) { %>
        <div class="sticky-bar">
            <span>Join the hunt and help solve the mystery of Professor Emily Xander disappearance!</span>
            <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <script defer src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.12.1/js/all.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
